{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-remark-js","path":"/users/sre/README.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4d65ff02-03cb-5816-8419-de55285164a8","html":"<h1 id=\"site-reliability-engineering-sre-support\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#site-reliability-engineering-sre-support\" aria-label=\"site reliability engineering sre support permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Site Reliability Engineering (SRE) Support</h1>\n<p>This repository contains all the SRE (Site Reliability Engineering) principles and guidelines for managing the <a href=\"https://operate-first.github.io/\">Operate  First</a> services.</p>\n<h2 id=\"what-is-sre\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-is-sre\" aria-label=\"what is sre permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What is SRE?</h2>\n<p>SRE is a software engineering approach to manage operations for systems, applications and services. We use software as a tool to manage systems, solve problems, and automate operations tasks.</p>\n<h2 id=\"get-started\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#get-started\" aria-label=\"get started permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Get started</h2>\n<p>If you’d like to learn and get hands on experience with SRE practices, but aren’t sure where or how to start, let us help!</p>\n<ol class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Follow this link to find <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/support/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22\">beginner friendly issues</a>.</li>\n<li>Tag yourself in the issue</li>\n<li>Join the <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/operatefirst/shared_invite/zt-o2gn4wn8-O39g7sthTAuPCvaCNRnLww\">Slack</a> and let us know that you’re interested in helping by posting in the <code class=\"language-text\">#support</code> channel a short introduction of yourself and a link to the issue you’d like to complete.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>To learn more, check out the <a href=\"https://www.operate-first.cloud/operations/sre/incident-management/incident-management-procedure.md\">incident management procedures</a>, <a href=\"https://www.operate-first.cloud/operations/sre/incident-management/github-receiver-setup.md\">GitHub receiver setup</a>, learn to <a href=\"https://www.operate-first.cloud/operations/sre/incident-management/configure-prometheus-alerts.md\">configure Prometheus alerts</a>, or browse the <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/support\">GitHub repo</a>.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/SRE/blob/master/README.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null,"extraClasses":null,"banner":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4d65ff02-03cb-5816-8419-de55285164a8"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","1764348645","3000541721","3606484676"]}